==English==

===Pronunciation===
*flūtter /flʌɾŗ/
===Verb===
'''to flutter'''  (''intransitive'')
# to [[flap]] or [[wave]] [[quickly]] but [[irregularly]]
#(''of a bird or insect'') to flap the [[wing]]s without [[flying]]; to [[fly]] with a light flapping of the wings
'''to flutter'''  (''transitive'')
# to cause something to flutter
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''flutter'''
# the act of [[fluttering]]
# a state of [[agitation]]
# an [[abnormal]] rapid [[pulsation]] of the [[heart]]
#(''British'') a small [[bet]]